---
// Import necessary components/layouts if needed

import "../styles/global.css";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="description" content="SimplyEr1c's portfolio page" />
    <title>SimplyEr1c</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/public/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:ital,opsz,wght@0,14..32,100..900;1,14..32,100..900&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <Navbar />
    <main>
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <section
        class="relative bg-coolblue text-snowwhite min-h-screen flex flex-col items-start justify-end p-12 overflow-hidden"
      >
        <!-- Background image layer -->
        <img
          src="public/SadMachine11.png"
          alt="Background"
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40 pointer-events-none select-none"
          draggable="false"
        />
        <!-- Content layer -->
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div
            class="bg-snowwhite text-coolblue p-7 -skew-x-12 shadow-2xl rounded-lg"
          >
            <h2 class="text-6xl">¡Hola! Soy</h2>
            <h1 class="text-[48px] md:text-[5rem] font-bold mb-4 leading-none">
              SIMPLYER1C
            </h1>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section
        class="bg-snowwhite min-h-screen grid md:grid-cols-2 space-x-4 p-16 items-center justify-center p-12"
      >
        <article>
          <img
            src="https://picsum.photos/seed/er1c/400"
            alt="Profile Picture"
            class="w-64 h-64 rounded-full shadow-xl mx-auto mb-8"
          />
          <aside
            class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-start space-y-1 bg-snowwhite p-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg"
          >
            <h2 class="text-4xl text-center font-bold mb-4">About Me</h2>
            <p><strong>Date of Birth:</strong> September 12, 2001 🎂</p>
            <p><strong>Gender:</strong> Male ♂️</p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> Venezuela 🌐</p>
            <p>
              <strong>Interests:</strong> 🖌️ Illustration, 🧊 3D Modeling, 📷 Image/Video
              Editing, 🔲 Motion Graphics
            </p>
          </aside>
        </article>
        <p class="text-justify max-w-1xl mx-auto">
          ¡Hola! Soy Er1c, un ilustrador autodidacta que le gusta explorar una
          variedad de herramientas y técnicas para hacer obras de arte. Desde
          Raster, Vectores y Modelado 3D. Empecé aprendiendo con gráficos
          vectoriales en internet con 16 años. Años más tarde aprendí modelado
          3D e ilustración digital con plataformas de cursos online como
          Domestika y Udemy. Hago hincapié en el uso de software libre y de
          código abierto, favoreciendo alternativas a herramientas comerciales
          como Adobe Suite. Me gusta compartir mi visión del mundo a través del
          Arte y descubrir nuevas habilidades.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>
    <section class="bg-coolblue text-snowwhite min-h-screen p-12">
      <h2
        class="text-[48px] md:text-[8rem] font-bold mb-4 leading-none text-center"
      >
        GALLERY
      </h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-center">Just some random pics for now...</p>
      <div class="columns-1 sm:columns-2 md:columns-3 gap-4 space-y-4 p-4">
        <img
          src="https://picsum.photos/seed/choco/400"
          alt="Image 1"
          class="w-full mb-4 rounded-lg shadow-xl break-inside-avoid"
        />
        <img
          src="https://picsum.photos/seed/late/400"
          alt="Image 2"
          class="w-full mb-4 rounded-lg shadow-xl break-inside-avoid"
        />
        <img
          src="https://picsum.photos/seed/cup/400"
          alt="Image 3"
          class="w-full mb-4 rounded-lg shadow-xl break-inside-avoid"
        />
        <img
          src="https://picsum.photos/seed/mouse/600/400"
          alt="Image 4"
          class="w-full mb-4 rounded-lg shadow-xl break-inside-avoid"
        />
        <img
          src="https://picsum.photos/seed/keyboard/400/800"
          alt="Image 5"
          class="w-full mb-4 rounded-lg shadow-xl break-inside-avoid"
        />
        <img
          src="https://picsum.photos/seed/phone/500/500"
          alt="Image 6"
          class="w-full mb-4 rounded-lg shadow-xl break-inside-avoid"
        />
      </div>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>
